{"tid":902953,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小弟屌左左一條非主流的女","createTime":"2018-11-15T07:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T10:37:08.000Z","uid":100029,"like":54,"dislike":484,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"dc208ad4668ebdc9ffeb5054a44f1c017c1a6017","tid":902953,"uid":100029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:45:55.000Z","msg":"小弟屌左一條非主流的女 (唔講啦，唔想被人起底)，都屌左幾年，做愛次數都叫做可以獻下醜。如果俾我重新再來過，我會選擇屌返主流既女 或者比較多人屌的女，原因如下:<br />\n被別人看不起，好多人覺得你有現家呢個成就是因為呢條女少人屌，所以你先可以屌到佢，無視我為呢條女付出的努力和時間，無視我係背後所經歷的所有野。付出的野可能同屌主流女的差唔多，但得到的野求遠都俾佢地少，地位俾佢地低。<br />\n總結: 係香港，屌非主流女慘過食屎。我自己就中左伏，返唔到轉頭。奉勸想向屌非主流女發展的人，三思而後行。"},{"pid":"9f62f68f113e5dd81c34f8e621f222e8e4eb07ad","tid":902953,"uid":140309,"like":128,"dislike":5,"score":123,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:47:52.000Z","msg":"TB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e6dada088fa784c9866935210bbcd367f5843d","tid":902953,"uid":69484,"like":95,"dislike":8,"score":87,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:48:49.000Z","msg":"有得屌已經贏左好多人啦"},{"pid":"e982814a7e43519cffd4691be25919d085196a48","tid":902953,"uid":163554,"like":100,"dislike":4,"score":96,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:48:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e7f7d7af25f15bee7c4a19a1048dc2df54e9ec1","tid":902953,"uid":149938,"like":259,"dislike":2,"score":257,"quote":{"pid":"9f62f68f113e5dd81c34f8e621f222e8e4eb07ad","tid":902953,"uid":140309,"like":128,"dislike":5,"score":123,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:47:52.000Z","msg":"TB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:50:03.000Z","msg":"Catgirl <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef2f3943953a482834363eb2c08e3eaad4fba10","tid":902953,"uid":100347,"like":210,"dislike":2,"score":208,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:51:48.000Z","msg":"R人問條女係咩非主流女"},{"pid":"1fc46fc266cdde700299ff9c785a4e2077bace3b","tid":902953,"uid":129042,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":