,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a8cdc6f0814b9a98df54d66780bc653cbbe5ecb7","tid":902953,"uid":192311,"like":166,"dislike":0,"score":166,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T04:18:33.000Z","msg":"我就食左一餐非主流的午餐 (唔講啦，唔想被人起底)，都食左幾個字，咬合次數都叫做可以獻下醜。如果俾我重新再來過，我會選擇食返主流既午餐 或者比較多人食的飯，原因如下:<br />\n被別人看不起，好多人覺得你有現家呢個成就是因為呢個餐少人叫，所以你先可以食到佢，無視我為呢個餐付出的努力和時間，無視我係背後所經歷的所有野。付出的野可能同食主流午餐的差唔多，但得到的野求遠都俾佢地少，地位俾佢地低。<br />\n總結: 係香港，食非主流嘢慘過食屎。我自己就中左伏，返唔到轉頭。奉勸想向食非主流嘢發展的人，三思而後行。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T09:17:13.000Z","msg":"喂哩個個夠膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 9/10"},{"pid":"5018c1a2c44ffb8cb61210a5cf5cbcd89b278310","tid":902953,"uid":13981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:08:08.000Z","msg":"我屌左個非主流老母"},{"pid":"deaaaab7f48bb0ed4ba9675b0e307e12f3efeaa9","tid":902953,"uid":13981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5018c1a2c44ffb8cb61210a5cf5cbcd89b278310","tid":902953,"uid":13981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:08:08.000Z","msg":"我屌左個非主流老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:08:25.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"9294cd46def3f7a7c2a786a425b6511286ffa847","tid":902953,"uid":13981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"deaaaab7f48bb0ed4ba9675b0e307e12f3efeaa9","tid":902953,"uid":13981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5018c1a2c44ffb8cb61210a5cf5cbcd89b278310","tid":902953,"uid":13981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:08:08.000Z","msg":"我屌左個非主流老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:08:25.000Z","msg":"唉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:08:45.000Z","msg":"係咪樓主老母？"},{"pid":"f4a8827dfba819851acbb6f06e35dcb1c07d8c4a","tid":902953,"uid":13981,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9294cd46def3f7a7c2a786a425b6511286ffa847","tid":902953,"uid":13981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"deaaaab7f48bb0ed4ba9675b0e307e12f3efeaa9","tid":902953,"uid":13981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"